{"tid":1009831,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"數據唔呃你！今鋪C朗完勝美斯喎！","createTime":"2019-02-05T12:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T18:01:35.000Z","uid":54373,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"90f918cd556556792b89850cef37375f19406d01","tid":1009831,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我話12m啫<br />\nC朗 5:2 美斯</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190204/photo/bkn-20190204231048832-0204_00882_001_01p.jpg?20190204231343\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20190204%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190204231048832-0204_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20190204231343&h=5ee15c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然話人比人，比死人，不過好似當今兩大球會美斯同基斯坦奴朗拿度，根本就係命中宿敵！兩位5屆世界足球先生以前喺西甲鬥餐死，以為今季C朗去咗意甲，不過一樣有傳媒拎佢哋嚟做比較。結果從數據睇，發現戰果同上季不變，阿根廷球王美斯又一次完勝葡萄牙球王C朗，大家又點睇呢個結果呢？ <br />\n<br />\n單睇今季，美斯已經入咗29球，而C朗只係得17個「士哥」。美斯另加14個助攻同89次關鍵傳送，C朗就慘慘豬只得7助攻同44次關鍵傳送。去到盤球推進，31歲嘅美斯有96次，33歲嘅C朗就只得33次，輸成條街囉。最後，美斯仲攞咗13次最佳球員獎，而C朗就只得7次，唔好唔記得，季初美斯仲曾經因傷抖咗3周，可以話係有多少讓賽，唯一C朗贏嘅，就只有佢幫「祖記」贏咗個意大利超級盃囉，不過點計呢鋪C朗都係輸得好徹底喎！ <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當然，唔少C朗球迷一定會幫口，話C朗新轉意甲要適應，同埋意甲出名防守勁，特別難踢，呢兩點都絕冇講錯，不過最慘係睇埋上季二人喺西甲數據，都一樣係美斯完勝喎！</span>好似美斯上季入34球、助攻12次、87次關鍵傳送，而C朗就只入26球、5次助攻、38次關鍵傳送。另外美斯有185次帶波同22次最佳球員獎，C朗就只有31次帶波同7次最佳球員，唯一解釋係上季皇馬好早放棄西甲，專注歐聯啦！ <br />\n<br />\n當然，講到底，睇一個球員有幾勁，唔可以單睇數據嘅，反正美斯同C朗就係當今兩大球會，大家都係把握機會睇多啲佢哋嘅好波好過啦！"},{"pid":"0d91e01df0163c42f309df9184c281c51fa35064","tid":1009831,"uid":46587,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"雞姦次數<br />\nC朗 1:0 美斯<br />\n又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6624d9c3f7cf4d2c1fd6003550710ef5e340d1af","tid":1009831,"uid":3454,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:59:46.000Z","msg":"米又系溫室小花<br />\n吾識英文呢一點就係鐵證<br />\n仲要牙朗幫佢做翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n還左翻譯費俾牙朗未牙"},{"pid":"3d04a58cad67c5b4f0cda9501d9a63b4d31335ee","tid":1009831,"uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:00:28.000Z","msg":"季初朗迷: 今季要比埋助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4580a75ae1f30b4d75caf9a126e8e661a84a706c","tid":1009831,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28f1357fd4ff293deeadd334869b6129d1e26ee","tid":1009831,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fdc18d867b1ea5af0d27af8c66907508ce1214","tid":1009831,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266c5e306ac245b8796d37156fa418546a10f8f1","tid":1009831,"uid":29929,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:19:37.000Z","msg":"王騎快d死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536a1574fc7b6718092a8151c5f31e42ec3fc7b0","tid":1009831,"uid":235263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f16a33869e43bb6728b8397944926c923aa4562","tid":1009831,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41fdc18d867b1ea5af0d27af8c66907508ce1214","tid":1009831,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:20:56.000Z","msg":"心起事成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081843c044ff8c23